  "text": "Therefore, one should carefully assess what is the equilibrium relevant to the specific problem at hand (nuclear fusion, radiative recombination, diffusion, etc.) and also consider, as also argued in [CITATION_1] Quarati (2000, 2006) , that non-Gaussian behavior in plasmas arises from all collective behaviors discussed above not only from non-equilibrium.",
